{"tid":400920,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"Credit呢啲野你地識條鐵咩","createTime":"2017-09-15T08:16:06.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-15T09:45:52.000Z","uid":55725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"9c121ff5f150bdd447e83b1a8ffc48fedf707a50","tid":400920,"uid":55725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:16:06.000Z","msg":"你地都知近日好多人講起IT抄黎抄去用左人地既野又唔肯落Credit<br />\n其實你地知唔知咩撚野係credit，唔識咪學下人地Gaming界係點樣Credit囉<br />\n我今日想講既係呢隻大家講得好撚垃圾既game The Division究竟係點落Credit<br />\n首先啲大野一定要credit，apple用FaceFX咪唔使成條街都面容扭曲囉<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mediafire.com/convkey/a296/11ab371ddj0032lzg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediafire.com%2Fconvkey%2Fa296%2F11ab371ddj0032lzg.jpg&h=aff9b8e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n之後黎料啦，原來小眾opensource都要credit，openssl都要credit呀死未<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mediafire.com/convkey/3215/tlj3muhrs46zpp9zg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediafire.com%2Fconvkey%2F3215%2Ftlj3muhrs46zpp9zg.jpg&h=e09dfdc1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mediafire.com/convkey/f6ae/xgcrhe31jf6z3f3zg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediafire.com%2Fconvkey%2Ff6ae%2Fxgcrhe31jf6z3f3zg.jpg&h=ec307d0d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJenkins都要credit架，你今日credit左未?<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mediafire.com/convkey/af1a/0l3n3ilri3n16puzg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediafire.com%2Fconvkey%2Faf1a%2F0l3n3ilri3n16puzg.jpg&h=df6293d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n麻煩credit埋字型呀唔該<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mediafire.com/convkey/edda/46dkpracn9r3bpxzg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediafire.com%2Fconvkey%2Fedda%2F46dkpracn9r3bpxzg.jpg&h=4f799df7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nCode4Food，你間公司整既字型終於有人記得落credit啦<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.mediafire.com/convkey/ea2a/qv6d30xzie34ln2zg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.mediafire.com%2Fconvkey%2Fea2a%2Fqv6d30xzie34ln2zg.jpg&h=ca8fae5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n咁做web個班人點解唔肯開番版野叫&quot;Credit&quot;<br />\n做web既垃圾係咪唔識落credit?<br />\n我見Gaming界好撚高質隻隻menu都有&quot;Credit&quot;呢版架<br />\nCredit呢啲野你地識條鐵咩"},{"pid":"1fbc53c51be35ea905f4d58a6da4c758a4217782","tid":400920,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:33:15.000Z","msg":"o下, 唔通......C4F係o係Adobe度做? 唔係掛! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW, 咁即係Credit=鳴謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S.  對Gaming界零認知! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b0c15d64be7fdb50be29b069ad2f299024c7823","tid":400920,"uid":55725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:35:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>o下, 唔通......C4F係o係Adobe度做? 唔係掛! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW, 咁即係Credit=鳴謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S.  對Gaming界零認知! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n字係上圖係下，可能我表達有啲問題"},{"pid":"b5e58958bdc1ab68322fd172600aa592d3ef1294","tid":400920,"uid":33883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:40:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>o下, 唔通......C4F係o係Adobe度做? 唔係掛! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nBTW, 咁即係Credit=鳴謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nP.S.  對Gaming界零認知! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n字係上圖係下，可能我表達有啲問題</blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOIC, 嚇得我丫!"},{"pid":"751a30d10d5ec5ae31622b4c46710763d5e45cbf","tid":400920,"uid":105553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-15T08:50:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>o下, 唔通......C4F係o係Adobe度做? 唔係掛! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.g